Subject: lag phase [MCO:0000364]
Value: a growth phase in which growth rate is null

Subject: acceleration phase [MCO:0000365]

Subject: retardation phase [MCO:0000367]

Subject: stationary phase [MCO:0000368]

Subject: phase of decline [MCO:0000369]

Subject: early exponential phase [MCO:0000370]

Subject: early to mid exponential phase [MCO:0000372]

Subject: late exponential phase [MCO:0000373]

Subject: mid to late exponential phase [MCO:0000375]
